If you wanna power both esp and LN287N on same battery
connect GND of LN298N to ESP32 GND
connect 5V of LN298N to ESP32 Vin/5V

Finally Connect the power source of 12V
--> +ve of Battery to 12V of LN298N
--> -ve of Battery to GND of LN298N ( REMEMBER GND IS CONNECTED TO -VE OF BATTERY AND GND OF ESP32)
